{"tid":1176763,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港咁多地方有七人足球場 但唔將啲場合併做十一人場","createTime":"2019-05-29T12:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T12:02:56.000Z","uid":59491,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a9db50552029228fe3ede74d6b6bad191a7b2ff8","tid":1176763,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"香港好多地方都係一個場入面有兩個七人場 (好似1,2號場咁分)<br />\n<br />\n根據規劃署 兩個七人場嘅尺寸 大約等同一個十一人場<br />\n咁既然係咁 點解唔將呢啲七人場合併做十一人場呢 再鋪下人造草<br />\n咁職業球員咪多啲地方練波<br />\n啲細路又可以早啲接觸真正嘅足球 唔會俾咩五人 七人足球嘅踢法踢壞腳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgk2LN1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbgk2LN1.png&h=c4677dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">規劃署 康樂、休憩用地及綠化規劃標準 p.20<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pland.gov.hk/pland_tc/tech_doc/hkpsg/full/pdf/ch4.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pland.gov.hk%2Fpland_tc%2Ftech_doc%2Fhkpsg%2Ffull%2Fpdf%2Fch4.pdf&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=25d8d1c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pland.gov.hk/pland_tc/tech_doc/hkpsg/full/pdf/ch4.pdf</a></span>"}]}